snippet.title: Miracle World - Fushigi no Kuni no IQ Meiro [Psx] - Intro
snippet.description:
Miracle World: Fushigi no Kuni no IQ Meiro is a game in which the player take part of a TV quiz game called Miracle World Brain Power, in which he will have to answer different questions and in some trials he will have to find 5 errors in the screens before the time limit ends. The game takes the player brain to the limit and is a very challenging game since the faster player wins.

The game features more than 1500 questions and also a 2 player vs mode. 

Device:
Playstation Classic
Bleemsync 1.2
OTG
Sandisk Cruzer Blade 128 GB

Capture:
Ezcap 284 hd video capture
